channel.description:
[center][size=64pt][img]http://puu.sh/iMzr9/8c76d73b25.png[/img][/size]
OS-Relapse is an old school private server based on spawn pking. we do not target one faction of players we are welcoming to all, we have full pvm and skilling aswell. we are currently in a beta stage and looking to expand to grab a slightly larger player base for the moment to allow us to fine tune the server to the way it deserves to be!
Highly active developer with 24/7 up time allows the maximum amount of fun!
we currently have working bounty hunter, full gwd, all OSRS items!
we are a ::master and ::pure style pking server with premade spawns aswell as ::item and ::getid commands!
